prc / pauserecording          Pauses or resumes the current recording

   Format:
      ;prc                    Pauses/resumes recording

   Notes:
      If a recording is in progress, pauses it; if a recording is paused,
         resumes recording.
      See the help for the ';record' command for more information about
         recordings.

   User commands:
      prc / pauserc / pauserecording
